# Local dev secrets for wrangler / CF Vite plugin.
# Copy to .dev.vars and fill in values before running `npm run dev`.
#
# DASHBOARD_KEK
#   Base64-encoded 32 random bytes. Used to AES-GCM-seal the gateway admin key,
#   the super-admin TOTP secret, and each merchant API key before they are
#   written to KV. Generate with:
#     openssl rand -base64 32
#   Rotating this value invalidates every sealed blob — only do it alongside a
#   dashboard re-onboarding.

DASHBOARD_KEK="replace-me-with-openssl-rand--base64-32-output-32-bytes-b64"
